description.en: This stylish Soul Dancer has some wicked moves! He also follows his owner around picking up dropped items.
description.ar: This stylish Soul Dancer has some wicked moves! He also follows his owner around picking up dropped items.
description.br: Este estiloso Dançarino de Soul tem alguns movimentos perversos! Ele também te segue e ajuda a pegar itens caídos.
description.cns: 这位时髦的灵魂舞者有一些邪恶的动作！他也能跟随他的主人并捡起周围掉落的物品。
description.de: Stets gut gelaunter Begleiter welcher mit dir läuft und swingend deine Items einsammelt.
description.fi: This stylish Soul Dancer has some wicked moves! He also follows his owner around picking up dropped items.
description.fil: This stylish Soul Dancer has some wicked moves! He also follows his owner around picking up dropped items.
description.fr: A le voir se trémousser en ramassant les objets, on sait pourquoi le métier de ramasseur-danseur avait disparu.
description.id: Soul Dancer memiliki beberapa jurus kejam! Dia juga mengikuti pemiliknya berkeliling mengambil barang-barang yang dijatuhkan.
description.it: This stylish Soul Dancer has some wicked moves! He also follows his owner around picking up dropped items.
description.jp: このジョニーはスタイリッシュなソウルダンサーですが、時々あやしげな動きをします。でも、ドロップしたアイテムを拾ったりもしてくれます。
description.kr: 이 세련된 Soul Dancer는 사악한 움직임을 가지고 있습니다! 그는 또한 자신의 주인을 따라 떨어 뜨린 물건을 줍기도합니다.
description.nl: This stylish Soul Dancer has some wicked moves! He also follows his owner around picking up dropped items.
description.pl: This stylish Soul Dancer has some wicked moves! He also follows his owner around picking up dropped items.
description.ru: Элвис жив! Хотя, если судить по цвету кожи, этот Элвис как раз-таки мертв. Тем не менее, он с удовольствием будет подбирать для вас предметы.
description.sp: ¡Este elegante Bailarín del Alma tiene algunos movimientos perversos! También sigue a su dueño y recoge los objetos soltados.

description.th: Soul Dancer ที่มีสไตล์นี้มีท่าเต้นที่ชั่วร้าย! เขายังเดินตามเจ้าของไปเก็บสิ่งของที่หล่นลงมา
description.vi: Soul Dancer phong cách này có một số bước di chuyển xấu xa! Nó cũng đi theo chủ nhân của mình để nhặt những món đồ bị đánh rơi.
